<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Wechat on Aimer's Blog</title><link>https://aimerneige.com/en/tags/wechat/</link><description>Recent content in Wechat on Aimer's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.153.1</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Nov 2022 12:03:30 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aimerneige.com/en/tags/wechat/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Install WeChat on Fedora</title><link>https://aimerneige.com/en/post/linux/install-wechat-on-fedora/</link><pubDate>Thu, 10 Nov 2022 12:03:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://aimerneige.com/en/post/linux/install-wechat-on-fedora/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="install-wechat-on-fedora"&gt;Install WeChat on Fedora&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="install-wine"&gt;Install Wine&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install wine
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="adjust-dpi-config"&gt;Adjust DPI Config&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use bellow command to open winecfg&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;winecfg
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adjust the dpi to a suitable value at tab &lt;code&gt;Graphics&lt;/code&gt;. (4k monitor, 192 dpi)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="download-and-config-fonts"&gt;Download And Config Fonts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Run the following commands&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install cabextract
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install winetricks
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;winetricks corefonts gdiplus riched20 riched30
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="download--install-wechat"&gt;Download &amp;amp; Install WeChat&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just download the exe Installer. (Same with download it from browser.)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>